Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:24.30,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the skies that are still unknown to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:28.39,Default,op,0,0,0,,I know, you're doing just the same -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:29.98,Default,op,0,0,0,,Dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.24,Default,op,0,0,0,,Just a small glow\NFrom those great days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:38.12,Default,op,0,0,0,,Is what dragging you along
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:41.87,Default,op,0,0,0,,Giving you faith and some comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:45.79,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the sun that scorches badly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:52.17,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only want to see your guise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.91,Default,op,0,0,0,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.18,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only watch \NWith tears on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:04.77,Default,op,0,0,0,,As you slowly disappear in this noon haze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.76,Default,op,0,0,0,,We're alone \NWe're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.31,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Walking this world on our own
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.36,0:01:16.53,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}Looking for each other since long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:22.48,Default,op,0,0,0,,In the end, in the end, \NAfter the day we finally meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:27.00,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord1\blur1\t(2100,2200,\shad3\blur3\c&HABADD8&)}We won't ever have to say "Goodbye"
Comment: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP END}
Comment: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP END}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:02:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dashing game, dear viewers!\NAnother set point is being played already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki is aiming to finish the match quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it!\NRyuzaki wins the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Ryuzaki, is there anyone, \Nyou want to dedicate this victory to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I dedicate it to Ms. Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My present shape would have not been possible \Nwithout Oka's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In this tournament, of all the girls,\Nshe was the most challenging opponent for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:48.63,Default,ep title,0,0,150,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HE3C4A2&\t(0,1100,\bord0.11\blur0.4\3c&H945431&)\c&HF7EEF0&\fnGabriola\fs78\frz359.6}Episode 1 \N\N\NI'm even more convinced, I love you      {\fax-0.85}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a dream.\NAs well as everyone experienced feeling lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to take a first step to the dream, \Nlest you start bogging down in everyday routine little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens, \None is bound to lose himself in that bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One needs some courage to do this, \Nyet he has to be not excessively reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then eventually if you are brave enough, \Nyou will end up trying to become reckless anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Easy to say,{And still, } Chiba...\N- You are no exception! {You can do it too.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,While your dream is still in sight, you put your every effort into it. \NThat's right, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At what time do you expect Oka to come here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At 2 she is free from her studies. \NAt 3 we have a training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce, Coach Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They are public relations executives from "Sanyu" inc{/ trading company}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They were the most persistent about being introduced to you, \NOka's full-time coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How may I be of service? {What is the nature of your business here?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal of our visit is to inquiry Mr. Katsura's intentions \Nand if your answer is positive,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the rest of our executives will schedule \Nan additional visit to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite being eliminated in the second round \Nat the recent Japan Open,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,your trainee impressed us greatly \Nwith her significant abilities and prospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We are convinced that she fits our corporate image perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to annual contract payment, our company will cover any expenses inflicted by attending the matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean Oka will have to transfer to pro league?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. \NOur company will provide an extensive backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, \NOka will make a first-class tournament pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Oka. You're free for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But we usually do a hundred more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you're good to go.\NRest is part of the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me say just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit acting like some pesky peddlers. \NPlayer is not a merchandise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, who were the people filming us{/ from earlier}? \NThey observed our practice closely{/ for a long time}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind them.\NJust old acquaintances of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.64,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Munakata Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Daigo. \NWill you have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if it won't bother you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,an eventful day, Munakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come when we no longer mention you \Non a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong, \Nbut I'm happy with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Oka, Todo, and Madam B. \Ncan now cope with your death in their everyday lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The sore spot you occupy in their hearts \Nshrinks and dims more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether they like it or not, \Nthose fellows will have to blaze their own way from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And it appears they are finally starting to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, are you sure? Won't you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please prepare a hot bath for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it, and still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't run every morning, \NI feel bad for the rest of the day{/ I will get out of shape}. Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka... Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Roadwork sure is hard under such heavy rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold! \NYou're soaking wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave me a shock. \NIt was the first time I saw you looking so lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was in the middle of training. \NHad nothing else on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You should not apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the most clear-headed person I know, \Nthe most composed. And also kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You are equally bright, strong and good at tennis!\NAnd also handso—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... I was so shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Oka. \NNow I'm even more convinced I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.92,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Ryuzaki Mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika, isn't it time for you to come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I was just about to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,According to our news informants,\NJapan's leading sports equipment manufacturer Sunstar,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as a certain foreign commodities and food producer \Nboth announced offering you a sponsorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:30.13,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Ryuzaki Reika - Aspiring Amateur Tennis Player
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you intend to sign a contract with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you maybe have a concrete plan \Nfor your transfer to a pro league?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you become a pro, does that mean your official record-setting \Namateur win streak will stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For the moment, I still have nothing concrete to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have indeed been approached with contract talks, \Nbut have not yet responded to neither of the sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can judge matters concerning me turning a pro \Nonly after having conferred them thoroughly with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can decide on your turning to pro \Nonly after conferring with me, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for exalting me, Reika.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But in reality you have had it decided since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so? \NMy eyes do not deceive me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, since you understand this yourself, \Nplease rid me of further questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo is a whole other thing.\NHe submitted a withdrawal from the university tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he will also drop out of the third year of university.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No clue. I was also notified just today \Nby a report from university.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the summer remembers the map, \Nyet it's about to hide behind that horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whilst my memories are frozen inside a glacier of rusty colors,\Nthrough which countless days and nights have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman, why are you acting so morose? \NYou know I've already paid a fortune for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent last eight years in disgrace{humiliation} and moral decline{degradation}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That is more than enough for memories to fade{/ discolor} \Nlike an old photofilm{/ positive film} tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I had but to tuck the fleeting love in the box and ribbon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to enclose it in the back of a drawer, \Njust like some trifling woman thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:45.22,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}The Drama Club presents a play: \N"One Step to Midnight" \NStarring: Maki Aikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so good, Maki! \NI genuinely felt your character!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:13:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki, jokes aside! \NThat was an ingenious paraphrase!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no good at playing tennis, \Nso I figured I'd be good at playing roles.{so I joined the drama club to kill time.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a future actress superstar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like attending the "Park."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistaking reality for a dream come true \Nis a routine{/ routinal} occasion there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock-knock{ on wood}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,However, thy dreams are someplace far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink more and get drunk more \Nin the name of song, future and love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is it you want to tell me? \NYou called me out to have a talk with me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I want to talk about. \NI just felt like seeing you suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Your face suggested \Nyou may be up to something, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess your practices are as intense as ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Unabated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You are well-nigh a pro now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tennis career! \NHave you not thought about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you not care about your own future?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, becoming a pro is not such a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At least it is much more realistic \Nthan me becoming an actress superstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, closing subject — tennis news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Winner of the Japan Open Men's Championship, held this June, \NTodo Takayuki announced his transition to the pro league.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:25.76,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Todo Takayuki - tennis player
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,His plan includes dropping out of university \Nand leaving Japan in order to fight in the global pro-circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Now, the next section...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki is listening. Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprising call! Long time no see. \NHow have you been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. What about you? \NYou have not been appearing a lot in "Park Hill" lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I will have to retire from tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's both joke and true. Fifty-fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Medical Faculty exhausts me completely. \NYeah, I wish I could play tennis daylong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this perplexes me just as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped seeing anyone and wanted to be left alone. \NI called his house several times, but to no avail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk to him, by any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He is embarking on some journey. \NHe will stay in Japan for something like two more weeks, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Oka? \NYou make junior mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For the next two weeks{ starting tomorrow} \NI won't be coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is your practice menu for those two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of hitting the ball, \Nfocus on enhancing your physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cut the corners{/ slack off} because you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In two weeks, you will have a physical fitness test. Until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but did something unexpected happen, Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare yourself effort and don't try to stop your Coach. \NIt's just a two weeks span.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you at least tell, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will return to the temple. \NI have some errand there only I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1500)}Thank you, Oka.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.74,0:16:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1500,0)}Now I'm even more convinced I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo Takayuki is entering the pro league.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He drops out of university and leaves Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Oka family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, has anyone called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Called you?\NNo, there was nothing of the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Not in any other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking?\NIs someone supposed to call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing of the kind. \NWell, okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:31.51,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Todo Takayuki \NIsamu Ozaki \NTakashi Chiba
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For such an occasion, \NI don't mind dialing. {/ even calling is fine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Todo. For the moment, I am not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for having to call you out to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it from Ozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You had more luck{/ success} than anyone else reaching{/ contacting} Todo \Non the current matter. Please, share it, Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have indeed reached him, \Nbut he never spilled anything concrete to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He merely reassured me this is his personal matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you at least share his current whereabouts then? \NI'm sure, as his friend, you are aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am aware of it. \NHowever, he has already started running{/ embarked on his journey}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Whether I prevail{/ succeed} or fail miserably{/ lose}, until I return to Japan again, \NI don't want to see anyone." That's how he expressed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the product of thorough consideration \Nand his solid determination.{He has been preparing for it for a long time and could finally come to a decision.} That is how it appears to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After graduating from Nishi High, \Nwe've lost Coach Munakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears, since then, everyone has been going their own way, \Ndistancing from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Somehow it seemed to me \NI'm the only one left behind on the court of Nishi High. {This line perplexes me deeply but there's no room for misinterpretation, I don't see what else she could mean by that}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true, Madame Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Hiromi feels being left behind as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way the mere two weeks of whetting{/ tampering} a rusty{/ dull} blade \Nwould make any difference{/ yield any result}. Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you everything I know, regardless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at your service!{I will do my best!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In tennis, it's not the passed test that makes you a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone can go ahead and announce their transition to pro.\NSend a notice to association — you're already a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But to fight in the global circuit major matches, \Nyou need to prove with your actions you're a real pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, are you prepared to go to the extremes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The wall between you and the world of men's tennis is high. \NWould you be able to get over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want to prove you wrong!{/ I still am not going to retreat!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Todo! In two weeks you will pass your pro test \Nand become a pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you have to conduct trainings by yourself lately. \NIs it going fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I strive for the best no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Having that said,\Nit still feels a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can address me anytime. \NI hope you don't mind practicing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? \NThanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, maybe it's just a rumor,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but are you planning to become a pro as well?\NAlong with Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Had that been so, you'd be the first one to know, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Attracted by Coach Munakata at the center, \Nwe have all entered this tennis solar system. {With Coach Munakata in the center, everyone congregated in tennis.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:22.67,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:28.30,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:31.26,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings mixed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.26,0:22:34.14,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:39.33,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:46.24,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:51.62,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.62,0:22:58.50,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:04.92,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:14.11,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:19.31,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.31,0:23:22.36,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:25.40,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:30.93,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aikawa Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're now on our way to the seaside training camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna make the most of\Nour 19th summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But for Hiromi this summer will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo suddenly takes the undreamed path.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, to do this, Todo even asked Coach Katsura for a special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Coach, why do you keep saying that Todo is not young enough now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.61,0:24:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming soon: "My 19th summer."
